{"tid":2009724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(整合懶人包)令政府冇銀用手段","createTime":"2020-05-10T03:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T11:28:53.000Z","uid":326037,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"59f2c28fca5e71d5c02163b6a015d5c1e5b9042c","tid":2009724,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:21:49.000Z","msg":"政府冇銀用 一籌莫展<br />\n<br />\n用盡每一個方法駛政府錢拉挎政府敗政，有機會/合資格拎綜援的人可以試下申請 唔駛再怕人嫌棄<br />\n<br />\n搞到政府冇錢先係攬炒主要目標，冇錢就冇能力推行反人權的政治理念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PzQLV7O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPzQLV7O.png&h=fae87be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒公務員)政府冇錢比人工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2009167/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2009167/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒國企藍店)永續黃圈 民主消費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2001434/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2001434/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒銀行)唔夠美金 大陸金融有流動性陷阱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2000285/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2000285/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒流動支付)唔用支付寶吸唔到香港人血<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1979144/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1979144/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒金融流動性)冇美金印唔到錢借唔到出去救經濟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1439205/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1439205/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒人民幣)數碼人民幣買唔到外國貨只能國內消費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2008253/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2008253/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n(反攻香港)建立海外武裝反政兼逃生 養流亡義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2007554/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2007554/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(攬炒經濟)數碼經濟轉型 反送中生機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2003600/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2003600/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"db985127e129d2ee3717a9cf9ba971fedca346b4","tid":2009724,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:26:51.000Z","msg":"Agree 橫掂大陸人都係咁攞冇理由香港人唔攞"},{"pid":"cbe49ed65ca243d50bf9869726c4482f6fa0b737","tid":2009724,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db985127e129d2ee3717a9cf9ba971fedca346b4","tid":2009724,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:26:51.000Z","msg":"Agree 橫掂大陸人都係咁攞冇理由香港人唔攞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:29:26.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔起"},{"pid":"ed3bd93a48a1a68fb49fa25f9bd5ca7ec0e6e8d6","tid":2009724,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"(懶人包)攬炒大全整合"},{"pid":"b2ce8633d0756595a94826e44582e9d66e750dbc","tid":2009724,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:52:05.000Z","msg":"(攬炒外史)全球最大全民抗極權經驗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2009192/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2009192/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"b1a58b7999c8ed972b54023ed46a170869431b94","tid":2009724,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T13:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd7581a751e3e0c8021f68fc5f38b113eef8d24","tid":2009724,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T15:43:04.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"9ee2790bd865389538fa7c02472d39284df4e2ac","tid":2009724,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:03:02.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"9d4b84022989f1c6664604478a07e7a50f15d933","tid":2009724,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:04:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e5752b95e01ea38d1f5faf75120605820522e3a","tid":2009724,"uid":247945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2